\f1\fs26 \cf2 \cb4 mpu_init()
\f0\fs28 \cb3 :\
\
* Wire.begin()\
* Wire.setClock(400000)\
* Wake MPU from sleep (write 0 to PWR_MGMT_1 register 0x6B)\
* Set gyro range: \'b1500 deg/s (register 0x1B, value 0x08)\
* Set accel range: \'b14g (register 0x1C, value 0x08)\
* Delay 100ms\

\f1\fs26 \cb4 mpu_read()
\f0\fs28 \cb3 :\
\
* Read 14 bytes starting at register 0x3B (accel XYZ, temp, gyro XYZ)\
* Combine high/low bytes into int16_t\
* Gyro: divide by 65.5 to get deg/s (\'b1500 dps range sensitivity)\
* Accel: divide by 8192.0 to get g (\'b14g range sensitivity)\
* Assign to:\
   * gyro_pitch_dps = gyro_x (or whichever axis is pitch in your mount)\
   * gyro_yaw_dps = gyro_y\
   * accel_pitch_deg = atan2(accel_x, accel_z) * 180.0 / PI (tilt angle from accel)\
   * accel_yaw_deg = atan2(accel_y, accel_z) * 180.0 / PI\
   * accel_mag_g = sqrt(accel_x\'b2 + accel_y\'b2 + accel_z\'b2)\
* Note: Add comment "// TODO: verify axis mapping matches your IMU mounting orientation"\
Servo write helper\cb1 \
