\f1\fs26 \cb4 compute_iae(df, launch_idx, burnout_idx)
\f0\fs28 \cb3 :\
\
* Extract burn window: df[launch_idx:burnout_idx]\
* time_s = timestamp_ms / 1000.0 - launch_time_s\
* IAE_pitch = trapz(|kalman_pitch_deg|, time_s)\
* IAE_yaw = trapz(|kalman_yaw_deg|, time_s)\
* IAE_total = IAE_pitch + IAE_yaw\
* Phase-segmented IAE:\
   * ignition: 0 to 0.3s\
   * peak: 0.3s to 0.6s\
   * tail-off: 0.6s to burn end\
* Return dict with all values\

